    public abstract class BasicMenu
extends java.lang.Object

      • BasicMenu

        public BasicMenu(com.badlogic.gdx.graphics.g2d.SpriteBatch spriteBatch,
                 java.lang.String titlePath,
                 java.lang.String[] menuOptions)
        Creates the viewport,stage and calculates padding value for each item in the screen.Also calculates the title position and size and generates each menu option as a button and stores it in the menuButtons list.
        Parameters:
        spriteBatch - spriteBatch
        titlePath - The file path of the texture to be used as a title
        menuOptions - A string array of menu options (An array of the text that will appear on buttons)
